<span id="freeTextContainer16479037828027314901">I adored this book so much. I read it in one sitting and I didn&apos;t stop reading until 2am this morning! It was an easy-going read with a not-so-brilliant plot but amazing characters. I forgot just how much I loved Levithan&apos;s writing. </span>
  <span id="freeText16479037828027314901" style="display:none">I adored this book so much. I read it in one sitting and I didn't stop reading until 2am this morning! It was an easy-going read with a not-so-brilliant plot but amazing characters. I forgot just how much I loved Levithan's writing. </span>
