        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1724741016" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15713733667774092631">DNF at page 125.<br/><br/>I tried. I tried so much to finish this book, but I just could not turn another page. <br/><br/>I&apos;m not saying it&apos;s a bad book, it&apos;s really good, but it&apos;s just not for me. I can&apos;t bring myself to feel anything for these characters or the story, no matter how much I forced myself to read. </span>
