<div id="review_2366626386" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2366626386" />
    <a title="Matthew Stefan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/69207991-matthew-stefan"><img alt="Matthew Stefan" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1555523618p2/69207991.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2366626386?book_show_action=true">Jun 18, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Matthew Stefan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Matthew Stefan" href="/user/show/69207991-matthew-stefan">Matthew Stefan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2366626386" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7989203169421549697">Overall a really cute book, if not a little predictable. It was a sweet little read and it made me smile. I&apos;d definitely recommend this one if you are needing a light and bubbly little romance. Despite having instalove and a love triangle, overall this was an enjoyable read. Noah and Paul are so cute together!</span>
  <span id="freeText7989203169421549697" style="display:none">Overall a really cute book, if not a little predictable. It was a sweet little read and it made me smile. I'd definitely recommend this one if you are needing a light and bubbly little romance. Despite having instalove and a love triangle, overall this was an enjoyable read. Noah and Paul are so cute together!</span>
